June 1978, L=... Lyn Hejinian writes:
 
"In such are we obsessed with our own lives, which lives being now
language, the emphasis has moved.  The emphasis is persistently
centric, so that where once one has sought a vocabulary for ideas,
now one seeks ideas for vocabularies".
 
 
